name: Postal Violet
description:
Do you want to know me?
I still can’t get my other half back.
There is nothing pure in this land.
All this sadness is insignificant.
I hope you like ice cream as much as I do.

My voice is so twisted.
Human life will always be miserable.
This body is the one of a monster.
Of all the people I know, nobody really listens to me.

Why are we making a toast?
Cold, ruptured words, alone in this land.
I want to have happy days.
